{
  "stem": "2581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They showed it in the Warsaw Ghetto where the Germans caught them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time, there were no border-- there were no wires outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could have smuggled in through a number of ways.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were Jewish policeman standing and-- and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this was-- this was a set up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They let these boys take the potatoes, and they were waiting for-- follow-- they must have followed them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because when they came in the ghetto, they stopped them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They opened their shirts and the potatoes fell out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they arrested these two boys, and a few days later, they took the entire town out to the fields and-- outside the town and hung these two young boys in front of everybody, everybody would see.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they started to take by groups people and send away in work camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from time to time, we heard that people died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No one-- we didn't know if they were shot or whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have seen the conditions of the-- you know, of the living conditions constantly deteriorate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we heard terrified, horrible stories of what is happening about those people that are being sent away from other towns.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No way, in no way, because people were-- people from our town ran away to the Russian side of the-- of the side of the Russians that occupied Poland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came back saying how bad it is there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we so these people coming back swollen, filthy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So why should we run?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And besides, we lived in a vicinity where you didn't expect any help from the Poles-- from our Polish neighbors.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
